Wingull (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0277: Swellow
Pokémon
#0279: Pelipper →

Wingull has been featured on 13 different cards since it debuted in the EX Ruby & Sapphire expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Wingull cards are normally Water-type or Colorless-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Wingull

Wingull
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
